{"tid":471112,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD Ryzen Threadripper 榮獲 CES 2018大獎","createTime":"2017-11-17T03:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T03:19:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"850001ead546980a0730fb86760640d315f970af","tid":471112,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"AMD宣布其高效能、為狂熱級玩家製造的Ryzen Threadripper 1950X處理器榮獲CES 2018電腦硬體與零組件類別最佳創新大獎。評審團由獨立產業設計師、工程師以及媒體工會成員組成，在28個類別中評鑑出尖端的消費性電子產品，表彰其在設計與工程方面的卓越成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.ctimes.com.tw/news/2017/11/14/1804058800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctimes.com.tw%2Fnews%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F1804058800.jpg&h=17b06e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ctimes.com.tw/DispNews-tw.asp?O=HK1BEAR9L80SAA00NL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctimes.com.tw%2FDispNews-tw.asp%3FO%3DHK1BEAR9L80SAA00NL&d=j3GOyvcuxBwnVifK%2BrcsgPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=00d7b7e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ctimes.com.tw/DispNews-tw.asp?O=HK1BEAR9L80SAA00NL</a></div>"},{"pid":"e7b7fbe9d06852481080b823e9fe7886c79caf21","tid":471112,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"作為全方位處理核心，AMD Ryzen Threadripper 1950X 建基於AMD強大的「Zen」核心架構，支援16核心與32執行緒，為要求最嚴苛的開發商、生產性消費者、創作者以及狂熱級玩家創造世界級效能。這款高階處理器針對最艱鉅的任務與工作負載提供強大的處理能力、毫無受限的潛力及無與倫比的效能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"aa6db302eb2974a5115ac466cb1d57fb9000d59c","tid":471112,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"AMD首席行銷長John Taylor表示，AMD Ryzen Threadripper 自推出以來廣受狂熱級玩家與專業評論者的一致好評，彰顯AMD整個工程團隊研發這款突破性產品的傑出表現。如今隨著榮獲CES 2018創新大獎，Ryzen Threadripper更突顯它在處理器創新歷史上的特殊地位與領先優勢。"},{"pid":"924ec6954ecf6f8c81bc82b78b31519aff01dc85","tid":471112,"uid":101219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"重點係比牙膏廠知道依家佢唔係大曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8aaff74379476ca85351e78cf04a9b823a597e5","tid":471112,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}